Rowdy Wolf/Megatron:





Rowdy Wolf glared down on KitKat from atop a boulder he was standing 
on. He aimed his rifle at her. He listened to her, but with no 
emotion. 

"I remember who you are," he said. "Is it true what Terrorsaur has 
said. Is Quickstrike dead?"




Megatron soared forward, he was just ahead. He could see Rowdy Wolf 
and KitKat.
